    "Many extensions are possible for ATLA.",
    "For instance, We design a new variation ATLA-K that learns an adversarial suffix from a set of {(Q, R) k } K k=1 in Appendix I.",
    "Also, ATLA can easily get composed with other jailbreaking methods like TAP, PAIR or GPTFuzzer to create new attacks.",
    "Besides, ATLA's query efficient property makes it possible to generate many jailbreaking suffixes fast, enabling the future development of targeted mitigation.",
    "This paper presents ATLA, an automated solution for generating jailbreak prompts."
